<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>WhatsApp QR Code</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .qr-box {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            min-height: 300px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        #qrcode_box {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        
        .loading {
            color: #667eea;
            font-size: 18px;
            animation: pulse 1.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }
        
        .info {
            background: #e3f2fd;
            color: #1976d2;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .steps {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .steps ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .steps li {
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: #4caf50;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .refresh-info {
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üîê WhatsApp API - QR Code</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Escaneie o c√≥digo abaixo com seu WhatsApp</p>
        
        <div class="qr-box">
            <% if (qrcode && qrcode !== '') { %>
                <img src="<%= qrcode %>" alt="QR Code" id="qrcode_box" />
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="loading">
                    <p>‚è≥ Gerando QR Code...</p>
                    <p style="font-size: 14px; margin-top: 10px;">Aguarde alguns segundos</p>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        
        <% if (qrcode && qrcode !== '') { %>
            <span class="status">‚úì QR Code Pronto</span>
        <% } %>
        
        <div class="info">
            <strong>üì± Como conectar:</strong>
            <div class="steps">
                <ol>
                    <li>Abra o <strong>WhatsApp</strong> no seu celular</li>
                    <li>Toque em <strong>Mais op√ß√µes</strong> (‚ãÆ) ou <strong>Configura√ß√µes</strong></li>
                    <li>Selecione <strong>Aparelhos conectados</strong></li>
                    <li>Toque em <strong>Conectar um aparelho</strong></li>
                    <li>Aponte a c√¢mera para este QR Code</li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <p class="refresh-info">
            <% if (!qrcode || qrcode === '') { %>
                üîÑ Esta p√°gina ser√° atualizada automaticamente a cada 3 segundos
            <% } else { %>
                ‚ö†Ô∏è O QR Code expira em alguns minutos. Se n√£o funcionar, atualize a p√°gina.
            <% } %>
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // Auto-refresh se o QR Code ainda n√£o foi gerado
        <% if (!qrcode || qrcode === '') { %>
            setTimeout(function() {
                location.reload();
            }, 3000);
        <% } %>
        
        // Verifica se o QR Code foi carregado
        const qrImg = document.getElementById('qrcode_box');
        if (qrImg) {
            qrImg.onerror = function() {
                console.error('Erro ao carregar QR Code');
                setTimeout(function() {
                    location.reload();
                }, 3000);
            };
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
